snippet.title: The Sims 3 Supernatural Producer Walkthrough
snippet.description: Get an in-depth look at werewolves, vampires, fairies and witches in The Sims 3 Supernatural Producer Walkthrough video! Learn more about spellcasting, alchemy, and discover what other spooky surprises await in the new world of Moonlight Falls. The Sims 3 Supernatural Expansion Pack is coming to PC on September 4, 2012!
